      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：子图Pezkuwi包含PezkuwiNode和PezkuwiRuntime，两者标签都是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic；外部FRAME虚线连Runtime，PezkuwiSDK虚线连Node。方向用从左到右LR布局对吗？",
