      "utterance": "对的，LR布局。不过PezkuwiSDK和PezkuwiNode的标签要区分清楚——PezkuwiSDK的标签是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，PezkuwiNode和PezkuwiRuntime都是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic。",
